# Scoreboard Testing

1. Run app
2. Check **Career Stats** Panel
3. Input Player names
    - Add P3
    - Add P4
    - Remove P3
4. Throw some dice
5. Score 7 for both A players
6. Pass the dice
7. Score 1 for both B players
8. Undo score for both B players
9. Score 2 Clink points for B player
10. Score 1 Paddle point for B player
11. Pass the dice
12. Score 2 Paddle Clink points for B player
13. Score 7 Clink points for A player
14. Pass the dice twice
15. Send to SnappaDB